    {
      "id": "PopularPost261317",
      "post_content": "The mana curve is so perfect in M13:  \n  \nTurn 1 - [Goblin Arsonist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist) (or other 1-cost goblin)  \nTurn 2 - [Krenko's Command](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko's Command)  \nTurn 3 - [Fervor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fervor)  \nTurn 4 - [Krenko,](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko,) tapping for 4 1/1 goblins attacking.  \n  \nThere is no doubt in my mind that they reprinted this to suit Krenko. Or more-so, made Krenko suit Fervor.",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost261317\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">The mana curve is so perfect in M13:<br/><br/>Turn 1 - <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin Arsonist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Arsonist\">Goblin Arsonist</a> (or other 1-cost goblin)<br/>Turn 2 - <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krenko's Command\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko's Command\">Krenko's Command</a><br/>Turn 3 - <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fervor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fervor\">Fervor</a><br/>Turn 4 - <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krenko,\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko,\">Krenko,</a> tapping for 4 1/1 goblins attacking.<br/><br/>There is no doubt in my mind that they reprinted this to suit Krenko. Or more-so, made Krenko suit Fervor.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '261317'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54405\">Ferlord</span>\r\n                                (8/6/2012 8:50:06 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRatin