    {
      "id": "PopularPost349562",
      "post_content": "This is a decent card, simple and straight-forward. And it can't bite you in the ass.  \nBut if you *really* have to get the tempo right away, consider [Mass Hysteria](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mass Hysteria), which gives haste globally but costs ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol) less.  \n  \nA compromise in between for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) is [Emblem of the Warmind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Emblem of the Warmind), which gives the same effect as Fervor,  \nbut comes with the drawback of being much more prone to destruction since it's an aura,  \nso its lifespan is bound to the creature of yours you enchant it with.  \n  \nRunning a ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol) deck? Consider [Fires of Yavimaya](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya) instead, which can also be turned into a +2/+2 boost when needed.  \n  \nIf you're just in for the ![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol), you'll probably want to take a look at [Thousand-Year Elixir instead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thousand-Year Elixir instead).",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost349562\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">This is a decent card, simple and straight-forward. And it can't bite you in the ass.<br/>But if you <i>really</i> have to get the tempo right away, consider <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mass Hysteria\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mass Hysteria\">Mass Hysteria</a>, which gives haste globally but costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/> less.<br/><br/>A compromise in between for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Emblem of the Warmind\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Emblem of the Warmind\">Emblem of the Warmind</a>, which gives the same effect as Fervor,<br/>but comes with the drawback of being much more prone to destruction since it's an aura,<br/>so its lifespan is bound to the creature of yours you enchant it with.<br/><br/>Running a <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/> deck? Consider <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fires of Yavimaya\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fires of Yavimaya\">Fires of Yavimaya</a> instead, which can also be turned into a +2/+2 boost when needed.<br/><br/>If you're just in for the <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Tap\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=tap&amp;type=symbol\"/>, you'll probably want to take a look at <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thousand-Year Elixir instead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thousand-Year Elixir instead\">Thousand-Year Elixir instead</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '349562'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (11/3/2013 1:11:50 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n            